What are you doing?

324
00:16:43,586 --> 00:16:45,003
HART: This is an authentic
first-edition.

325
00:16:45,004 --> 00:16:46,922
You don't understand the magic

326
00:16:46,923 --> 00:16:48,173
and the mystery of this girl.

327
00:16:48,174 --> 00:16:51,511
"I have been waiting for this
my whole life."

328
00:16:52,053 --> 00:16:54,681
It's what Somerset Maugham
says in that thing, you remember?

329
00:16:56,474 --> 00:16:57,474
- Me?
- HART: Yeah.

330
00:16:57,475 --> 00:17:01,396
"There's always one who loves
and one who lets himself be loved."

331
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,647
That's the truth, isn't it?

332
00:17:03,648 --> 00:17:04,898
Of course, you know you're in trouble

333
00:17:04,899 --> 00:17:06,400
when you're looking
