338
00:17:20,290 --> 00:17:21,416
HART: My interests?

339
00:17:22,625 --> 00:17:24,544
So now you're going to analyze me?

340
00:17:25,128 --> 00:17:27,005
Thank you, Doctor Bacardi.

341
00:17:27,881 --> 00:17:30,299
Look, I met her at rehearsals
