00:18:38,243 --> 00:18:40,829
Sixteen dollars. Plus delivery.

370
00:18:42,455 --> 00:18:45,624
"Dick, I've got a beautiful feeling,
everything's going your way.

371
00:18:45,625 --> 00:18:46,959
"Love, Dorothy."

372
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:48,628
She's quoting Oscar?

373
00:18:55,718 --> 00:18:59,721
I write with her husband for 24 years,

